## other versions:
- [Fabric version](https://modrinth.com/mod/project-se-fabric)

## what this mod adds:
- New portal;
- New blocks;
- New recipes;
- New ore;
- New tree;
- New structures;
- New armor;
- New items;
- New food;
- Green Hills it self;
- new flower;

## HOW TO MAKE A PORTAL:
- Needs 14x gold (for the portal frame);
- And RING (custom item crafted with 8x gold ingot in crafting table like a chest);

## ORE:
BluedIron:
- Info- BluedIron only generates in GreenHills and is pretty strong;
- Smelted in furnace;
- Can make tools and armor;
- Cinda common;

## FOOD:
Only food in this mod in cooked leaves;
- Get leaf block (from green hills biome) and cook it in the furnace;
